summary: This is an FBI 302 form documenting a proffer interview conducted on September 9, 2019, with an individual named ARROYO at the U.S. Attorney's Office for the Southern District of New York. The interview was attended by multiple law enforcement and prosecutorial personnel. The main body of the interview notes is heavily redacted and appears to be in a non-standard format or possibly corrupted/encrypted, making the substantive content largely unreadable.
